---
title: Speedy Cajun Style Chicken and Bacon Macaroni with Spinach and Italian Style Cheese
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Speedy Cajun Style Chicken and Bacon Macaroni in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R13_W44_UK_QR15792-3_MAIN__add_low-59278bf5.jpg
